data.description: Presenting a rare and elegant three-story Colonial home in the heart of pristine Ardsley Village, Westchester. This large home is centrally located, making it convenient to enjoy everything the area has to offer while still being outside of the hustle and bustle of New York City.  Nestled in the thriving community of Ardsley, this home seamlessly blends with the natural surroundings, offering picturesque views from every corner. Abundant natural light graces each level, with the soothing sight of swaying trees visible from the kitchen windows, dining room sliding doors, the strategically positioned deck, and the Master Bedroom.  The open kitchen boasts a generous island/breakfast bar that flows into the dining room, extending further onto the deck. This space, with its park views, exudes a countryside ambiance, making it perfect for hosting gatherings, from backyard fire pit soir es to outdoor movie nights or quiet moments alone on the deck.  The ground floor features a walk-in Family Room, complete with an additional bedroom or home office (ideal as an in-law suite), complemented by a summer kitchen and a private bathroom.  Ascending to the second level, the formal living room seamlessly connects to the dining room with deck access. The spacious, sunlit kitchen, equipped with modern stainless steel appliances, awaits your culinary creations. All of this is just steps away from Ardsley's distinguished Blue Ribbon schools and Pascone Park, the epicenter of community activities, including Food Truck Fridays, the Summer Concert Series, 5K Marathons, and sports facilities.  The private Master Bedroom offers an en-suite bathroom and two closets, including a walk-in. Two additional generously sized bedrooms grace the third level, making this home versatile for various dynamics.  From every vantage point, find serenity and tranquility in your personal oasis just beyond the city limits. Ideal for Metro-North commuters, with Grand Central Station less than 30 minutes away, this property is the embodiment of a coveted suburban lifestyle.  Do not miss this exceptional opportunity to acquire the home you've been waiting for. It is destined to be in high demand.
